<F P=102>  SK2201062094 Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 21 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2201062094 </F>
<F P=104>  Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Summary] According to the statistical data provided by the 
provincial statistical bureau, in 1993 the industrial 
enterprises at or above the township level throughout Hebei 
Province realized 162.1 billion yuan of total output value 
calculated in current prices, which showed a 17.53 percent 
increase over 1992 and ranked the province 14th in the country. 
The rate of production and sale among their products reached 
98.19 percent; this ranked the province third in the country 
behind Shanghai and Tianjin municipalities. 

